data.description: **Price Reduction** Motivated Seller **  Property is sited in a desirable community located minutes away from downtown. This beautiful 3 bedroom 2 bath home is move in ready and awaiting the perfect buyers to call home. Kitchen offers crown molding, granite countertops, and dark brown cabinets along with a smart refrigerator. The oversized bonus room can be used as a dining room, office, or family room perfect for entertaining guest. Plenty of backyard space with vinyl fencing. Living Room has a built in custom entertainment center with LED lights and an electric fireplace. Front porch/entry-way is screened in and the back porch is enclosed with windows and tile flooring. This community is quiet and well kept; perfect for a growing family with a community playground area. Located in the Estate of Lake Alfred and minutes away from local schools and major highways.    Don't miss your opportunity to schedule your showing today!
